			<div class="content" id="post-content-776012">
									

<p>My brain is spinning in five different directions, trying to make sense of that statement.</p>
<p>About the story: Best. Self-insert fic. Ever. As soon as I read the part about Green Able and 682 turning yellow, I knew that Character-Bibs had gone Green Lantern on us. So, 682 will someday be neutralized by one of the SCP Cliches ("lol superhero") and 423 is an O5. Wow. *brain explodes*</p>
<blockquote>
<p>…the quiet sound of a paradigm shifting without a clutch.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Where have I heard this line before…</p>
<p>Edit @ below post: Now I remember. "Paradigm shifting without a clutch" was a line from a <em>Dilbert</em> strip a few years back. Dogbert killed an Accounting Troll by wearing a hat backwards, and the line was his explanation for "that popping sound".</p>

							</div>

								
